Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:41.45,song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Čuje se tapkanje noža po daščici.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:46.29,song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tofu se njiše levo-desno dok jaja pokušavaju da izmaknu.{\i0}
