Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:01.47,song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}sakupi sav pirinač u činiju{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:05.06,song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}i sve je spremno za doručak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:09.23,song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vreme je za ustajanje.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:12.90,song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sada, kada su se svi sakupili za stolom,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:16.82,song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}hajde, jedimo koliko nam srce ište.{\i0}
